2:16:35.583 --> 2:16:38.833
-[Norma Jeane] Not here. Not in this bed.
-[president grunting]

2:16:38.916 --> 2:16:41.833
-[Norma Jeane] Don't cough. Don't gag.
-[president grunting forcefully]

2:16:41.916 --> 2:16:43.833
[Norma Jeane] You have to swallow.

2:16:43.916 --> 2:16:47.416
-You have to swallow.
-Oh, you dirty girl… [gasps]

2:16:48.166 --> 2:16:50.083
Oh, baby! [moans]

2:16:51.750 --> 2:16:54.583
[panting] Yes. Ah, fantastic.

2:16:55.458 --> 2:17:00.125
[grunting]

2:17:00.208 --> 2:17:02.500
[panting]

2:17:28.916 --> 2:17:31.083
[sighs deeply]

2:17:34.166 --> 2:17:38.208
[man over telephone]
Mr. President… Mr. President…

2:17:39.833 --> 2:17:41.708
These women, Mr. President…

2:17:43.500 --> 2:17:44.958
These allegations,

2:17:46.666 --> 2:17:49.375
they inflict irreparable harm on America.

2:17:52.500 --> 2:17:53.708
Mr. President.

2:17:55.208 --> 2:17:56.250
Uh…

2:17:56.333 --> 2:17:57.166
[exhales]

2:17:59.500 --> 2:18:02.583
Gee, Pronto, these girls?

2:18:02.666 --> 2:18:03.750
[sighs]

2:18:03.833 --> 2:18:06.291
Gosh, I know you're a man of the world.

2:18:06.791 --> 2:18:08.416
I'm not a child. [chuckles]

2:18:09.208 --> 2:18:11.000
You don't have to worry about me.

2:18:11.083 --> 2:18:12.208
-[president gasps]
-[exclaims]

2:18:12.291 --> 2:18:14.708
[ominous music playing]

2:18:17.291 --> 2:18:19.583
[agent 1, distortedly]
Monroe… Miss Monroe.

2:18:20.375 --> 2:18:21.583
Come on. Just get up.

2:18:21.666 --> 2:18:23.625
-Get up. Get… Just… [grunts]
-[coughing]

2:18:23.708 --> 2:18:27.166
-[agent 2] Oh, Jesus. Grab her.
-[agent 1] I got her. Come on.

2:18:29.625 --> 2:18:33.375
Miss Monroe, this way, ma'am.
Do you need assistance?

2:18:42.416 --> 2:18:44.083
I love the president.

2:18:47.625 --> 2:18:49.083
I love the president.

2:19:03.875 --> 2:19:06.291
[urinating forcefully]

2:19:06.375 --> 2:19:07.500
[exclaims]

2:19:07.583 --> 2:19:09.166
[knock on door]

2:19:09.250 --> 2:19:10.208
[agent 2] Ma'am?

2:19:10.916 --> 2:19:13.416
No. I'm fine.

2:19:14.375 --> 2:19:16.208
Don't come inside, please.

2:19:17.500 --> 2:19:19.833
[urine trickling]

2:19:38.208 --> 2:19:40.250
[shrieks]

2:19:41.916 --> 2:19:42.958
[Whitey] Oh!

2:19:43.458 --> 2:19:45.458
Miss Monroe! What's wrong? What's wrong?

2:19:45.541 --> 2:19:48.208
Oh, gosh, Whitey. I thought I was dead.

2:19:48.291 --> 2:19:50.250
-You just dozed off.
-Just for a second.

2:19:52.208 --> 2:19:54.208
[both laughing]

2:19:54.291 --> 2:19:55.791
Oh God.

2:19:55.875 --> 2:19:57.083
Oh, stop.

2:20:01.791 --> 2:20:04.083
And you thought you were… You look dead.

2:20:04.875 --> 2:20:08.166
-I need this.
-My God. Have it.

2:20:08.250 --> 2:20:10.541
[Norma Jeane laughing]

2:20:11.791 --> 2:20:12.750
You all right?

2:20:13.375 --> 2:20:14.583
Stop screaming.

2:20:17.083 --> 2:20:17.916
[exhales]

2:20:18.000 --> 2:20:20.458
[both laughing]

2:20:36.708 --> 2:20:39.375
[ethereal music playing]

2:20:47.833 --> 2:20:49.875
[telephone ringing]

2:21:12.083 --> 2:21:14.583
[ringing continues]

2:21:25.833 --> 2:21:27.083
[Norma Jeane] Who is it?

2:21:28.250 --> 2:21:30.625
[static crackles, whistles]

2:21:31.791 --> 2:21:33.375
[telephone slams onto receiver]

2:21:45.208 --> 2:21:48.833
[ominous music playing]

2:22:06.625 --> 2:22:07.708
[gasps]

2:22:11.500 --> 2:22:14.708
[breathing heavily]

2:22:28.083 --> 2:22:29.333
[dog barking]

2:22:48.416 --> 2:22:49.833
[ominous music intensifies]

2:22:53.416 --> 2:22:54.833
[thudding]

2:22:54.916 --> 2:22:56.708
[breathing heavily]

2:23:02.500 --> 2:23:03.541
[thudding continues]

2:23:06.500 --> 2:23:08.833
The circle of light is yours.

2:23:08.916 --> 2:23:13.041
You enclose yourself in the circle.
You carry it with you wherever you go.

2:23:13.125 --> 2:23:15.375
[thudding continues]

2:23:16.500 --> 2:23:18.791
The circle of light is yours.

2:23:18.875 --> 2:23:22.916
You enclose yourself in the circle.
You carry it with you wherever you go.

2:23:23.000 --> 2:23:25.250
-[footsteps approaching]
-[whimpering]

2:23:25.333 --> 2:23:26.583
[screams]

2:23:27.083 --> 2:23:29.833
[somber music playing]

2:23:50.416 --> 2:23:54.000
It's just a dream. It's just a dream.

2:24:00.000 --> 2:24:02.166
[sobs] It's just a dream.

2:24:02.250 --> 2:24:04.125
It's just a dream.

2:24:05.625 --> 2:24:07.625
[instruments clinking]

2:24:08.333 --> 2:24:10.958
It's just a dream. It's just a… [crying]

2:24:13.708 --> 2:24:15.375
[menacing music playing]

2:24:24.791 --> 2:24:26.375
[Norma Jeane laughs maniacally]

2:24:30.500 --> 2:24:32.541
It's just a crazy dream.

2:24:37.083 --> 2:24:41.041
[suctioning]

2:25:06.750 --> 2:25:07.708
[groans]

2:25:12.666 --> 2:25:13.708
[sighs]

2:25:18.375 --> 2:25:19.875
Oh Christ.

2:25:21.291 --> 2:25:23.083
What an ugly dream.

2:25:26.750 --> 2:25:27.958
[telephone ringing]

2:25:35.291 --> 2:25:36.958
What a crazy dream.

2:25:44.416 --> 2:25:46.541
[father] I have not intended to be cruel.

2:25:47.375 --> 2:25:48.875
Or to toy with your heart.

2:25:52.208 --> 2:25:54.666
I have been incapacitated by illness.

2:25:56.750 --> 2:25:58.583
But you are in my thoughts often.

2:26:03.916 --> 2:26:06.208
I have known you only at a distance.

2:26:07.291 --> 2:26:11.583
Years passed, and that distance
seemed too great to surmount.

2:26:15.916 --> 2:26:18.875
Time is like a fast river
running through us.

2:26:20.625 --> 2:26:22.041
Already it isn't.

2:26:24.208 --> 2:26:27.458
Soon I will contact you, I promise.

2:26:27.541 --> 2:26:31.125
Yes. Yes, but why are you waiting?

2:26:32.666 --> 2:26:34.208
[father] Your tearful father.

2:26:35.125 --> 2:26:36.541
[telephone ringing]

2:26:45.083 --> 2:26:47.333
-[line picks up]
-[Eddy over telephone] Norma…

2:26:48.000 --> 2:26:49.583
[breathing shakily]

2:26:49.666 --> 2:26:50.625
It's Eddy G.

2:26:51.958 --> 2:26:53.208
[tearfully] Cass is dead.

2:26:58.833 --> 2:27:03.541
Choked on his puke and strangled.
Classic alky death, huh?

2:27:04.458 --> 2:27:06.875
I found him when I came over this morning.

2:27:11.250 --> 2:27:13.250
Cass left a memento for you, Norma.

2:27:14.208 --> 2:27:15.250
[sobs]

2:27:16.708 --> 2:27:18.333
[Eddy] Most of his things, he left to me.

2:27:18.416 --> 2:27:22.291
I was his good buddy, never let him down,
so he left most of his things to me.

2:27:23.291 --> 2:27:24.750
But this memento…

2:27:25.416 --> 2:27:26.500
[breathing heavily]

2:27:26.583 --> 2:27:28.875
[Eddy] …"This is for Norma someday,"
he'd say.

2:27:31.750 --> 2:27:33.250
It meant a lot to him.

2:27:34.916 --> 2:27:37.791
"Norma always had my heart," he'd say.

2:27:37.875 --> 2:27:38.958
[breathes heavily]

2:27:42.500 --> 2:27:43.375
No.

2:27:46.083 --> 2:27:47.208
[Eddy] "No" what?

2:27:50.291 --> 2:27:51.250
[crying]

2:27:52.333 --> 2:27:53.625
I don't want it.

2:27:54.666 --> 2:27:56.333
I don't want it, Eddy.

2:27:56.416 --> 2:27:58.833
[Eddy] How do you know
you don't want it, Norma?

2:28:01.208 --> 2:28:02.541
You don't know what it is.

2:28:06.541 --> 2:28:09.916
Right, baby. I'll send it.

2:28:11.333 --> 2:28:12.833
Look for special delivery.

2:28:26.083 --> 2:28:27.166
[Norma Jeane grunts]

2:28:29.333 --> 2:28:30.333
Thank you.

2:28:31.666 --> 2:28:33.250
Oh, just a minute.

2:28:42.041 --> 2:28:43.416
Where's my wallet?

2:28:44.958 --> 2:28:46.125
Not in my purse?

2:29:00.166 --> 2:29:01.500
Where did I put it?

2:29:06.291 --> 2:29:08.625
[pensive music playing]

2:30:23.500 --> 2:30:24.500
Oh.

2:31:26.541 --> 2:31:27.791
[breath trembling]

2:31:39.083 --> 2:31:40.041
[gasps]

2:31:54.500 --> 2:31:55.833
[sobs]

2:31:55.916 --> 2:31:58.291
But you wanted baby dead too.

2:32:02.833 --> 2:32:04.416
You know you did.

2:32:08.500 --> 2:32:09.458
[cries]

2:32:24.041 --> 2:32:25.041
[sniffles]

2:33:10.000 --> 2:33:11.500
[gasping]

2:33:17.416 --> 2:33:18.333
[sobbing]

2:33:34.041 --> 2:33:35.583
[screams]

2:33:37.833 --> 2:33:39.416
[continues sobbing]

2:33:45.875 --> 2:33:47.583
[screams]

2:34:15.416 --> 2:34:17.541
[melancholy music playing]

2:37:09.625 --> 2:37:11.583
[mother] Norma Jeane, look.

2:37:14.958 --> 2:37:16.375
That man is your father.

2:37:55.500 --> 2:37:58.625
[birds chirping softly]

2:38:06.083 --> 2:38:09.000
[children chattering in distance]

2:38:32.291 --> 2:38:35.291
[chirping, chattering fade to silence]

2:38:39.291 --> 2:38:42.708
[ethereal music playing]
